VALUES ('9e513ad4-ca9b-4dd5-836d-f8c29b49b2e1', 'As used in the passage, "scrutinize" most nearly means', 'A longitudinal analysis of dataset 5826740 indicates that local conditions shape outcomes in ways that single-variable models often miss. Observers recorded consistent patterns across 3 measurement cycles, comparing baseline and intervention periods while holding unrelated variables stable. When the expected mechanism appeared, downstream indicators shifted in the same direction, suggesting the scrutinize is not merely correlational in this context. Community interviews and field notes repeatedly', 'passage', '[{"id":"A","text":"to worsen","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Collocation Decoy] \"to worsen\" contradicts the sentence logic requiring a provisional judgment."},{"id":"B","text":"to lessen or make less severe","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct (B). \"mitigate\" fits \"to lessen or make less severe\" given the provisional conclusion awaiting replication."},{"id":"C","text":"to ignore","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Flat Literal] \"to ignore\" contradicts the sentence logic requiring a provisional judgment."},{"id":"D","text":"to multiply","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Tone Inversion] \"to multiply\" contradicts the sentence logic requiring a provisional judgment."}]'::jsonb, 'B', 'Step 1 — Locate the word in context
